</dd> <dt id="fieldsetlegend-New"> New functions</dt> <dd id="fieldset-New">
<table class="invisible two_column_table">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>
<p align="center"><a class="external-link" href="http://www.bikalabs.com/portfolio/umhlathuze"><img alt="Umhlathuze logo" class="image-inline" src="http://www.bikalabs.com/images/umhlathuze" /></a></p>
<p>New items sponsored by the water quality lab at the City of uMhlathuze, Richards Bay:</p>
<a class="external-link" href="bika_setup/bika_calculations">Results calculations</a>,     including interim fields and dependent analyses, are user    configurable and new calculations can be added by authorised users<br /><br /> Dormant setup items can be de-activated, which will remove them from general view while maintaining database integrity. The same for sample and analysis request cancellation workflows<br /><br />
<p><a class="external-link" href="http://plone.org/">Plone 4</a>'s versioning is used to maintain references to historical data. Working copy support combined with  content locking  allow multiple users  access to data without conflicts</p>
<p>Using AJAX, Plone 4's user interface and a host of smaller enhancements, many clicks were saved and general performance improved</p>
<p class="callout"><b>Where did all the columns go?</b><br /><br />To facilitate tablet display screens, users select which columns they need for Samples, Analysis Request and Worksheet lists<br /><br /><b>Right click </b>on the column headers on these list to display the column display toggle menu</p>
</td>
<td>
<p class="callout" style="text-align: left; "><b>New in this upgrade</b> v3.0a2<br /><br />Besides numerous improvements and bug fixes, the v3.0a2 egg includes the following:<br /><br />Optional sampling and preservation workflows and roles<br /><br />Sample partitioning · Container &amp; preservation automation<br /><br />AR templates · Sample point &amp; Sample type restrictions<br /><br />Reports (framework only). The 'Analysis per service' report shows what is planned<br /><br />Improved i18n handling, and updated translation strings from Transifex. English, Afrikaans, Spanish (Castillian and Catalan) completed. Others well under way<br /><br />Numerous performance enhancements<br /><br />Analysis Service &amp; Method associations<br /><br />Improved Analysis Service and Method pop-up<br /><br />Currency selection from Zope locales<br /><br />Combined AR View and Edit tabs<br /><br />Re-factored AR 'Add/Remove Analyses' screen<br /><br />Append only remarks fields on more objects</p>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
